          <h2 style="color:var(--white);margin-bottom:8px;">Reserve a 7-Passenger Minivan</h2>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin-bottom:20px;">Tell us your dates and where you're headed. We'll set you up with the right rate.</p>
